oles\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another dance number featured three dancers, a woman and two men, who danced through the streets and were seen going up the stairs of a building, stopping as they began kissing.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another dance number\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"three dancers\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"two men\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the stairs\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"a building\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three dancers were then seen entering a room as they continued kissing until the door was shut.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The three dancers\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"a room\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaselet us knowif you are having issues with commenting.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Breitbart\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"score\": 0.9999938322338617, \"rank\": 6.167804118074305e-06, \"text\": \"Breitbart\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2110}]}]}"